@startuml
actor Customer
participant System
participant DiscountOfferService
participant BasketService

Customer -> System : Request list of discount offers
activate System
System -> DiscountOfferService : Get discount offers
activate DiscountOfferService
DiscountOfferService --> System : Return list of offers
deactivate DiscountOfferService
System -> Customer : Display list of offers
deactivate System

Customer -> System : Choose a specific discount offer
activate System
System -> DiscountOfferService : Get offer details
activate DiscountOfferService
DiscountOfferService --> System : Return offer details
deactivate DiscountOfferService
System -> Customer : Display offer details
deactivate System

Customer -> System : Click "Add to basket"
activate System
System -> DiscountOfferService : Check availability
activate DiscountOfferService
DiscountOfferService --> System : Return availability
deactivate DiscountOfferService
System -> BasketService : Add offer to basket
activate BasketService
BasketService --> System : Confirm addition
deactivate BasketService
System -> Customer : Update basket view
deactivate System

@enduml